General.Name: Suratwwala Business Group Limited
General.Description: Suratwwala Business Group Limited, a real estate development company, engages in the development and sale of residential and commercial projects in Pune, India. The company provides maintenance services for its developed properties, including housekeeping, security and guard, power backup to the occupants/residents, and other related services. It is also involved in the renting of space to internet service providers companies to install their system to provide internet and to other companies to advertise their products in the premises for their promotion and renting of the unsold space for short duration. Suratwwala Business Group Limited was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Pune, India.
